  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (COMPOUND-03 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Despite multiple credibility factors achieving levels substantially below their required levels, the assurance level is declared High and the decision is Accepted — an overstatement that triggers COMPOUND-03. Full 13-factor assessment is included; all assessed factors show achievedLevel strictly less than requiredLevel.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-mrl5",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/vad-hemolysis-cfd-credible",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/cfd-centrifugal-pump-hemolysis",
