    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The assessment team concluded that the Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification effort and the breadth of the 13-factor review collectively demonstrate sufficient credibility for regulatory submission. The team judged that the High assurance level is warranted given the volume of evidence gathered, notwithstanding individual factor gaps. This rationale does not address the systematic achievedLevel deficits across all 13 factors and constitutes an assurance-level overstatement consistent with COMPOUND-03.",
